Invocation Name: drupal upgrades
des: Ever wonder if your favorite Drupal module has been upgraded to Drupal 8? Now you can check! Using the official API on Drupal.org, Alexa will search to see if your module exists for Drupal 7 or Drupal 8.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
